---
title: Maple-Mustard Glazed Chicken Breasts with BBQ-Spiced Wedges and Sugar Snap Peas
description: You can't go wrong with classic Canadian flavours like maple and mustard. Potato wedges get tossed in BBQ Seasoning for added smokiness to complement the sweetness of the maple syrup.

